                        </span>
                        Authentication
                    </h2>
                    
                    <p class="text-gray-400 mb-6">
                        The LUCAS API uses API keys to authenticate requests. You can view and manage your API keys in the <a href="#" class="text-lucas-green hover:underline">Dashboard</a>.
                    </p>
                    
                    <div class="bg-lucas-card border border-lucas-border rounded-xl overflow-hidden mb-6">
                        <div class="px-5 py-3 border-b border-lucas-border flex items-center justify-between">
                            <span class="text-sm text-gray-400">API Key Format</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="p-5 font-mono text-sm">
                            <span class="text-gray-500">lcs_live_</span><span class="text-lucas-green">xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx</span>
